[01:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Wow - look at how far we have come in the last few&nbsp; years. These new results are still not perfect,&nbsp;&nbsp; but they are leaps and bounds beyond the Everybody&nbsp; Dance Now paper. And this is not only better,&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[01:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'but it also solves a significantly more difficult&nbsp; problem. You see, here, with your text prompt you&nbsp;&nbsp; can choose your background and your attire&nbsp; as you wish. No video of you is needed.'

